Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,other dimensions,\Nthings that are peculiar and unique,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,things that sound bizarre.\NThink about it. If it sounds bizarre,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you know why? Cuz it's bizarre.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange\Npeople get strange messages and then
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they start strange belief systems and\Nthey seem to lack no there's no der of
