Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,imagine. They're still waiting out in\Nthe desert for the UFO to pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?\NDid Jesus Christ say that? The Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,say it? Does Krishna say it? Did any of\Nthe great enlightened spiritual masters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of all time say anything about that? No.\NDid they say go home and do numerology
