Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus said, "That's the way I realized\NGod was I got a channeling from Master
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honky Punk and he told me to park out\Nthere and wait for the UFOs to pick me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,up\Nand he meantime eat nothing but grass."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I must cross my toes 14 times a day\Nover hickory nuts. I mean, the bizarre
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,crap that people believe, they haul into\Nmy office and they mail it to me and I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,say,\N"Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight and narrow is the way."\NYou don't need anything peculiar. You
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,don't need anything bizarre.\NYou don't need anything unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All of mankind is in agreement on\Ncertain basic facts. It's so obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that you really have to be quite\Nresistant to not see it. H and then pick
