Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of avoiding uh the truth is what what it\Nis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and they use it as an excuse you know\Nexcuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So the third eye then is the capacity\Nfor spiritual discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, wickedness is to prey upon the\Ninnocence of the naivity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and distort their capacity to perceive\Ntruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my definition of wickedness.\Ns to seduce the innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and brainwash them into believing\Nthat which is non-intigorous
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to serve your own selfish ends.\NThat is perversion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,degeneracy.\NSo, the Astral Circus is out there
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for you\Nand Sedona is right around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You get an oral reading within a block\Nof I'll tell you that somebody will
