Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's start a school of sheep\Nkneebones. the sacred sheep kneebones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can go how it goes back to\Nancient Ebiscinia and and manufacture a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,whole trip. See?\NAll right. Um, so the true spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,work is more mundane. Sounds mundane.\NDoesn't sound exciting, does it? Not
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,like getting a psychic reading. You know\Nwhat I mean?
