Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you.\NTell me about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you were walking there with the\Noxen and then your mother-in-law and you
