Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:20:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,entrancing story.\NWe even have pet psychics to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take we'll take Kitty for a\Nreading, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She was once a cat for Queen Nefertiti.\NI see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she ate one of the sacred mice and\Nhad to come back as a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What about love, romance, and sex? Yes,\Nwe don't talk much about that.
