Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.\NIt had nothing to do with love for a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,long time. It had to do with mating. Had\Nto do with animal nature. Had to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,um\NI was going to say recreation,
