Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.79,0:25:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,did not see it in the cold-blooded\Nreptilian world. You don't see it in the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.72,0:25:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,world of snakes. You don't see it in the\Namphibians.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.03,0:25:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins to emerge and it really\Nemerges in full flower in the mamlian
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.44,0:25:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,world with suckling and the mamlon\Nbonding that goes on. There you see the
