Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.12,0:26:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's a dead cat. uh to get her\Nlittle kitten safely from this roof to a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.84,0:26:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,tree.\NSo you see the nurturance then of life
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.08,0:26:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning to evolve. As time went on,\Nthe matingness between man and woman now
