Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.52,0:26:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,uh a canubial uh pleasure and she had no\Ngreat value in and of herself. Men and
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.67,0:26:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,women didn't hang out together. He\Ndevalued her. She stewed the pot and all
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.64,0:26:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that. But it was him that went on and\Nbrought home the bear. You know what I'm
