Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.44,0:28:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the alliance of nations, for the unity\Nof fortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.76,0:28:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Many parts of the world uh you know your\Nwife or your your spouse is picked out
